        <view class="_bd2">使用微信扫一扫，扫描屏幕二维码登录小程序，或者在箱门屏幕上输入手机号打开箱门。</view>
        <image class="step_sign" src="../../assets/images/home_nav/step_sign.png" mode="widthFix"></image>
      </view>
      <view class="sign_img">
       <image class="sign_img" src="../../assets/images/home_nav/step3.png" mode="widthFix"></image>
      </view>
    </view>
    <view class="about_item _right">
      <view class="sign_img">
       <image class="sign_img" src="../../assets/images/home_nav/step4.png" mode="widthFix"></image>
      </view>
      <view class="word_part">
        <image class="step_t" src="../../assets/images/home_nav/step4_t.png" mode="widthFix"></image>
        <view class="_bd1">投放物品并关闭箱门</view>
        <view class="_bd2">将物品分品类投入回收箱，投递完成之后关闭箱门。</view>
      </view>
    </view>
